entry.title: Ukraine Under New Missile Barrage as Russia Warns West About Tank Pledges
entry.content: Explosions rocked Kyiv, while officials in Moscow said the latest promises of Western military aid would escalate the conflict.

entry.title: In China, Young Women Become Accidental Symbols of Defiance
entry.content: A new generation of novice dissidents—many artists and writers—arrested after demonstrations against pandemic lockdowns is fueled by anger over a clampdown on freedoms and attacks on women’s rights.
